A little about our
Cozy Coffee Restaurant & Bar
Thank you for visiting our page, we would like to introduce ourselves. My name is
Casey
and I am the Co-Owner of
Cozy Coffee Cafe AKA Cozy Coffee Restaurant & Bar!
Here is a little about me and my family.
My wife
Matina
and I have been together for 19 years, she is my best friend and someone who will always have my back! Her and I will be working hard making sure that everything is the best possible while you are here!
Our mission is to make sure everyone starts the day off on the right foot. With a smiling face and a great cup of coffee that will taste the same every time you order. Of course, if you can't make it for breakfast, we now offer dinner, as well as a full bar!
We are looking forward to bringing some new programs into the community and making our Cafe a place where everyone "knows your name"!  We want to support our community so we will be bringing in new and exciting local item's!  Please come by and say hello!
Thank you again for all your support.
The
Cozy Coffee Restaurant & Bar
Family
